\section{Experimental Setups}
We trained and evaluated DDPG on the simulated Open AI Gym environment Pendulum-v0. Then we did the same on the Quanser simulated environments Qube-v0 (Furuta Pendulum), and the BallBalancerSim-v0. We used low-dimensional features (torques etc.) for all environments. No pixel data was used.
